<p><span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:left; background-color: #86b300; background:linear-gradient(to bottom right, #86b300, #5f8000); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">你能8能帮我个忙，把转换器连入局域网？<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup></span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:right; background-color: #0089e6; background:linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0089e6, #006ab3); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">Lana? 这个没问题，但还好吧？</span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:left; background-color: #739900; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #86b300, #5f8000); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">我很好，为甚这么问？<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-2')">2</a></sup></span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:right; background-color: #808080; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0089e6, #006ab3); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">呃，只是，你总是对我用字代替词非常不满&#8230;</span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:left; background-color: #739900; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #86b300, #5f8000); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">哦，哈，那是个奇怪的自动更正错误，我想我得把我手机送去检查了。</span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:right; background-color: #808080; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0089e6, #006ab3); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">好的吧。行，那我在把转换器连上去之后该做什么？</span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:left; background-color: #739900; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #86b300, #5f8000); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">你能加载虚拟环境吗？</span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:right; background-color: #808080; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0089e6, #006ab3); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">为什么?</span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:left; background-color: #739900; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #86b300, #5f8000); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">有个潜在的客户想看看AI在遇到一些刺激时会有什么反应。</span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:right; background-color: #808080; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0089e6, #006ab3); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">在这里的狗屎电脑上得花上差不多30分钟才能搞定。</span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:left; background-color: #739900; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #86b300, #5f8000); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">不用加载图形，它们只需要用声音刺激。</span></span><br />
<br />
<br />
<span style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 15px; padding: 4px 8px; display: inline-block; text-align: left; float:right; background-color: #808080; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0089e6, #006ab3); color: #fff;"><span style="text-shadow: #003 1px 1px;">那只要几分钟就好，我们会需要测试什么？</span></span><br />
